{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aac393c297","title":"考送学生章程","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4b336b96ff","index":0,"year":1927,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"aac393c297"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"791524435b","type":"paragraph","text":"考送学生章程","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"09ec4f2f31","type":"paragraph","text":"（1927年6月）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"3f7c1b7e43","type":"paragraph","text":"一、名额（各省名额见招生计划）不能超出规定数目，学生分配，以注重交通为要，政治中心，农运需要的地域，将该省总名额分配于各县。由县党部按照本章程，考送省党部。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"a63efe2d40","type":"paragraph","text":"二、资格，学生以由各县考送，来自乡间者为最好，其资格如与下列不合者，到所时绝不收录，并不负责造回","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"4bf4c23374","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、思想革命观点确定，无反动思想","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"d06fccfad5","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、学历中等学校毕业或建业者，高小毕业常识较优者，小学教师。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"474b58475b","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、决心向党部填具志愿书，决心入所后服从本所纪律，接受严格训练，毕业回到本省乡村做农民运动，无他障想者","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"353496ef36","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、身体强健耐劳，确无肺病、痔病、神经衰弱、花柳等病，及其他痛疾，在所能服严厉军操，到乡能走远路（省县党部须负责行个别严格检验）。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"b46ff9c811","type":"paragraph","text":"皮、年龄十八岁以上，三十五岁以下。已、性别一概男生。核","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"9e375b8bc2","type":"paragraph","text":"三、考试，由县党部考送省党部，省党部加以复试，以定去取。考试分笔试、口试。笔试科目：国文、口口、历史常识测验（本所口口复核如认为不合格即行遗退）。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"526263cc0b","type":"paragraph","text":"四、待遇来往川资，由所供给，每人口口元，不收学费。制服由所供给，单制服两套。毕业后派赴乡村，担负农民运动工作。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"a8db9f5aff","type":"paragraph","text":"五、学习期间九月一日开学","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"6b77e4d15e","type":"paragraph","text":"六、到所日期限八月二十七日起到三十一日止，为到所时间，退到早来，均不收纳","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"5c0353765a","type":"paragraph","text":"附学生须自行携带之物件表","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"e059f65823","type":"paragraph","text":"一、面盆、手巾、激口孟、牙刷。二、短夹裤、短棉衣、棉裤、换洗里衣。三、鞋袜、皮鞋。四、棉被裤全副。五、小箱口口。六、笔墨。七、洗衣剃头零用。上列各物必须自行携带齐全，如有缺乏本所概不供给。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"4afce5f941","type":"paragraph","text":"1927年6月18日，农讲所学员毕业，大部被委任为农民特派员，或回乡从事农民运动。图为农讲所发给学员的毕业证章。《送学员》（油画）代","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"},{"id":"ab313e23c9","type":"paragraph","text":"《红日照征程》（中国画）","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297"}],"page":{"id":"a862db1320","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"aac393c297","start":29,"end":33}}}},"__N_SSG":true}